      public void processCookies​(String cookieLog)
      This method takes in the cookie log we'd like to process, then goes through it to fill our internal data structures "occurrences" "maxOccurrenceNum", and "maxOccurrenceCookies". The format of our internal data structures will allow us to return the most used cookie per date later on...
